                           <desc>: Short prayer or antiphone (unidentified).</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#4va">4va</locus>: በእሁድ፡ ሰንበት፡ ወበ፱፡ በዓላት፡ በ ፮። ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡
                              ሃሌ፡ ሉያ</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#127rb">ff. 127rb-128</locus>
                           <desc>vb: Traditional commentary in Gǝʿǝz (?).</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#127rb">127rb</locus>: ለ፬ ዘይቤ፡ ልባዌ፡ አንብቦ፡
                              ዝማሬ፡...</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note is written in a careful hand; a few passages have been
                              washed out. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00"/>
                           <desc> </desc>
                           <desc>ff.129va-130ra: Daily prayers and litanies.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">f.122vb: ወካዕበ፡ ናስተበቍዕ፡ ዘኵሎ፡ ይእኅይ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡
