                           59r, 71r, 72r, 72v, 75r, 75v, 76v, 77r, 78v, 80r.
 - Crude notes:
                              <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>, 1v, 2r, 3r, 3v, 4r, 12r, 18v, 19r,
                           64v, 130r, 130va, 131r, 131v.
 - Crude drawings: <locus target="#2v">2v</locus>, 3r, 3v, 4r, 130v. 
 - Spaces for rubrication left
                           unfilled: <locus from="119vb" to="128vb">119vb-128vb</locus>
 - Crude
                           minor notes written with different hands partly in reddish-brown ink:
                              <locus from="130ra" to="132rb">130ra-132rb</locus>.</item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
